'''《新聞媒體議價法令》'''（{{lang-en|News Media Bargaining Code}}）<ref name="aph6652">{{Cite web|title=ParlInfo - Treasury Laws Amendment (News Media and Digital Platforms Mandatory Bargaining Code) Bill 2021|url=https://parlinfo.aph.gov.au/parlInfo/search/display/display.w3p;page=0;query=BillId:r6652%20Recstruct:billhome|accessdate=2021-02-20|work=parlinfo.aph.gov.au|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304101847/https://parlinfo.aph.gov.au/parlInfo/search/display/display.w3p;page=0;query=BillId:r6652%20Recstruct:billhome|dead-url=no}}</ref>又稱'''媒介议价法'''，是[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]]的一项法律，該法律規定在[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]运营的大型[[互聯網|互聯網]]平台展示澳大利亞当地新闻出版商出版的新聞內容時，必須向澳大利亞新闻出版商支付费用。2020年4月，澳大利亚政府要求{{link-en|澳大利亚竞争和消费者委员会|Australian Competition & Consumer Commission}}（ACCC）起草该法律，该法律遭到[[Facebook|Facebook]]和[[Google|Google]]的強烈反对<ref name=":1">{{Cite news|author=Barbaschow|first=Asha|title=Media Bargaining Code enters Parliament despite Google and Facebook's best efforts|date=2020-12-10|url=https://www.zdnet.com/article/media-bargaining-code-enters-parliament-despite-google-and-facebooks-best-efforts/|accessdate=2021-02-18|work=ZDNet|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210215080517/https://www.zdnet.com/article/media-bargaining-code-enters-parliament-despite-google-and-facebooks-best-efforts/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="accc202007">{{Cite web|title=News media bargaining code|url=https://www.accc.gov.au/focus-areas/digital-platforms/news-media-bargaining-code|accessdate=2021-02-21|date=2020-07-26|work=Australian Competition and Consumer Commission|archive-date=2021-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210319115404/https://www.accc.gov.au/focus-areas/digital-platforms/news-media-bargaining-code|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Google一度威脅離開澳大利亞市場。[[微軟|微軟]]卻支持該法案<ref>{{Cite web |title=科網巨企你們還可信嗎？ |url=https://www.sbs.com.au/chinese/cantonese/zh-hant/audio/news-media-bargaining-code |accessdate=2021-03-16 |author=Erik Cheung |date=2021-02-12 |publisher=SBS中文 |language=zh-hant}}</ref>。2021年2月18日，Facebook阻止澳大利亚用户在Facebook分享或閱讀新闻内容<ref>{{Cite news|title=Facebook news ban drops reader traffic to news stories by 13 per cent within Australia, Chartbeat data shows|first=Sophie|author=Meixner|date=2021-02-19|url=https://www.abc.net.au/news/2021-02-19/facebook-referral-traffic-down-news-ban-morrison-frydenberg/13171568|accessdate=2021-02-21|work=Australian Broadcasting Corporation|archive-date=2021-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324210158/https://www.abc.net.au/news/2021-02-19/facebook-referral-traffic-down-news-ban-morrison-frydenberg/13171568|dead-url=no}}</ref>。數日後，澳大利亚政府修改法案，Facebook和Google与澳大利亚政府达成协议，同意付費給澳大利亞新聞出版商，Facebook繼續允許澳大利亚用户分享和閱讀新闻<ref name="bbc21">{{Cite news|title=Facebook blocks Australian users from viewing or sharing news|date=2021-02-19|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-australia-56099523|accessdate=2021-02-21|archive-date=2021-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323030904/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-australia-56099523|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2021年2月25日，澳大利亞國會通過該法案<ref>{{Cite web |title=澳洲通過媒體議價法 Google臉書刊登新聞須付費 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202102250022.aspx |accessdate=2021-03-16 |author=李佩珊 |date=2021-02-25 |publisher=中央通訊社 |language=zh-hant |editor=張曉雯 |location=雪梨 |archive-date=2021-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225172418/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202102250022.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="cnbc-facebook-restore">{{Cite news|author=Choudhury|first=Saheli Roy|title=Facebook to restore news pages for Australian users in coming days|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2021/02/23/facebook-to-restore-news-pages-for-australian-users-in-coming-days.html|accessdate=2021-02-22|publisher=CNBC|date=2021-02-22|archive-date=2021-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210321154640/https://www.cnbc.com/2021/02/23/facebook-to-restore-news-pages-for-australian-users-in-coming-days.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。3月16日，Facebook向[[新闻集团|新闻集团]]支付费用，新闻集团則允許Facebook展示[[新闻集团|新闻集团]]旗下的媒體所报道的新闻<ref>{{Cite web |title=科技巨头的账单！默多克的新闻集团与脸书签署新闻付费协议 |url=http://www.ifnews.com/news.html?aid=140134 |accessdate=2021-03-16 |author=周秭沫 |date=2021-03-16 |publisher=国际金融报 |language=zh-hans |editor=程慧 |archive-date=2021-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210319080608/http://www.ifnews.com/news.html?aid=140134 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

